00:06:20.760 --> 00:06:22.600
Ya Tuhan...
- Tulsi...

00:06:25.400 --> 00:06:26.480
Tangkap!

00:06:34.280 --> 00:06:35.640
Hai...

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:37.040
Kemana kamu pergi?

00:06:47.200 --> 00:06:48.360
